{"tid":2100990,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"世衛設獨立小組檢討處理疫情手法及各國應變","createTime":"2020-07-09T12:31:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-09T12:46:01.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7c02b7d650d5077e07cb1a563c7dd5b0c3999526","tid":2100990,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T12:31:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1536829-20200709.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1536829-20200709.htm&d=LWtkxptWC%2F4RDCuqQUibmtMQoCHxbgs64DeXVNsql00%3D&h=895b0ca7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1536829-20200709.htm&h=73a04b0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1536829-20200709.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n世界衛生組織宣布成立獨立小組，檢討世衛處理新型冠狀病毒疫情以及各國政府的應變。<br />\n<br />\n總幹事譚德塞在視像會議宣布，新西蘭前總理克拉克和利比亞前總統瑟利夫同意領導小組。<br />\n<br />\n譚德塞說，現時是自我反思的時候，強調檢討不是例行公事，將認真對待。<br />\n<br />\n克拉克就說，今次任務極具挑戰性。<br />\n<br />\n美國政府前日正式展開退出世衛組織程序，總統特朗普多次批評世衛組織以「中國為中心」。<br />\n<br />\n全球至今超過1200萬人確診新型肺炎，近55萬人死亡。"},{"pid":"e54f3248f5f7bb50c9bbea146b74066f63a6e6d9","tid":2100990,"uid":273703,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T12:31:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a4f4436d431529d22cad1566abda27a8af8d8b80","tid":2100990,"uid":251732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T12:32:17.000Z","msg":"死黑鬼自己人查自己人"},{"pid":"1ef849849eb89119e226d3d752d061fad0f09fa5","tid":2100990,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T12:33:32.000Z","msg":"左手右手"},{"pid":"8627bef1b88da2a9c14996b40b661cf6fde92197","tid":2100990,"uid":61577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T12:41:29.000Z","msg":"垃圾<br />\n美帝唔退出都唔認衰"},{"pid":"2ac9f51f20ae05eb00d45897610920ad16a710b7","tid":2100990,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-09T12:46:01.000Z","msg":"直接結論：點解要支那人入境，學台灣就咩事都冇"}]}